-- Goldman, TPG Funds Buy Diaper Maker Ontex From Candover for $1.55 Billion
-- John Martens
-- 2010-07-15T15:12:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-15/goldman-tpg-funds-buy-diaper-maker-ontex-from-candover-for-1-55-billion.html

          
          
             GS Capital Partners LP and funds
managed by TPG Inc. agreed to buy Belgian diaper maker  Ontex NV 
from Candover Investments Plc for 1.2 billion euros, according
to an e-mailed statement from Ontex.  
 The transaction is subject to regulatory approvals and will
be completed before the end of the year, according to the
statement.  
          
          


  


        